    <summary>Specifies how a <see cref="T:System.Data.DataColumn" /> is mapped.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 The <xref:System.Data.MappingType> enumeration is used when getting or setting the <xref:System.Data.DataColumn.ColumnMapping%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.DataColumn>. The property determines how a column's values will be written when the <xref:System.Data.DataSet.WriteXml%2A> method is called on a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to write the data and schema out as an XML document.  
  
   
  
